Thought: Retrieve the AccountSid for the user from IdentityDirectoryEvents based solely on the UPN to get the SID.  
Action: execute[
SELECT DISTINCT AccountSid 
FROM IdentityDirectoryEvents 
WHERE AccountUpn = 'Jordan P@vnevado.alpineskihouse.co';
]

Thought: Query IdentityLogonEvents for any entries matching the user’s email domain to retrieve the SID.  
Action: execute[
SELECT DISTINCT AccountSid, AccountUpn, IPAddress 
FROM IdentityLogonEvents 
WHERE AccountUpn LIKE '%vnevado.alpineskihouse.co%';
]

